OL,3,CAdvice issued as norovirus cases spike
OL,4,Cin North West
OL,6,FHealth chiefs in the North West are
OL,7,Furging people to take action following
OL,8,Fa spike in norovirus cases in the
OL,9,Fregion.
OL,11,FThe NHS says an average of 164 people
OL,12,Fper day were in hospital with the
OL,13,Fvirus in the North West in the week up
OL,14,Fto January 25 - more than two-thirds
OL,15,Fhigher than the same week last year.
