OL,3,CAdvice issued as norovirus cases spike
OL,4,Cin North West
OL,6,FDr Paula Cowan, a GP and Regional
OL,7,FMedical Director for NHS England in
OL,8,Fthe North West, said: "Norovirus can
OL,9,Fbe a deeply unpleasant and
OL,10,Fdebilitating illness, especially for
OL,11,Fthose with underlying medical
OL,12,Fcondition, and it's vital people do
OL,13,Feverything they can to stop it
OL,14,Fspreading.
OL,16,F"Alcohol hand gels do not kill
OL,17,Fnorovirus, but you can prevent the
OL,18,Fspread of norovirus by frequent
OL,19,Fhandwashing with soap and water.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
