OL,3,CAdvice issued as norovirus cases spike
OL,4,Cin North West
OL,6,F"You can usually treat norovirus at
OL,7,Fhome by resting, drinking plenty of
OL,8,Ffluids and taking paracetamol if you
OL,9,Fneed it to bring down high
OL,10,Ftemperatures and ease any discomfort."
OL,12,FNationally, an average of over 1,100
OL,13,Fadult beds were occupied due to the
OL,14,Fvirus each day.
