OL,3,CAdvice issued as norovirus cases spike
OL,4,Cin North West
OL,6,FDr Merav Kliner, Regional Deputy
OL,7,FDirector, UKHSA North West, said:
OL,8,F"Norovirus activity has remained high
OL,9,Fin recent weeks in the North West.
OL,10,FSymptoms include nausea, vomiting and
OL,11,Fdiarrhoea, but can also include a high
OL,12,Ftemperature, abdominal pain and aching
OL,13,Flimbs.
OL,15,F"Norovirus infections can cause
OL,16,Fdehydration, especially in vulnerable
OL,17,Fgroups such as young children, older
OL,18,Fpeople and those who are
OL,19,Fimmunocompromised, so if you do get
OL,20,Fill it is important to drink plenty of
OL,21,Ffluids.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
