OL,3,CAdvice issued as norovirus cases spike
OL,4,Cin North West
OL,6,F"If you have diarrhoea and vomiting,
OL,7,Fit's really important to take steps to
OL,8,Favoid passing the infection on. Please
OL,9,Favoid visiting people in hospitals and
OL,10,Fcare homes to prevent spreading the
OL,11,Finfection in these settings.
OL,13,F"Do not return to work, school or
OL,14,Fnursery until 48 hours after your
OL,15,Fsymptoms have stopped, and don't
OL,16,Fprepare food for others in that time
OL,17,Feither."
