OL,3,CAdvice issued as norovirus cases spike
OL,4,Cin North West
OL,6,FIf you have symptoms of norovirus, the
OL,7,FNHS advice includes drinking plenty of
OL,8,Ffluids, staying at home with plenty of
OL,9,Frest, eating when able and taking
OL,10,Fparacetamol if needed.
